law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 27, sec. 5, effective June 20, 2005; and amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 513, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 168, sec. 1, effective July 13, 1990. -- Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 269, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988.

metadata.lrc-note: (6/20/2005). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 27 prevails over its amendment in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85.
